élorusse" lang="be" hreflang="be" class="interlanguage-link-target">Беларуская</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-be-x-old"><a href="https://be-tarask.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%86%D1%81%D0%B0%D0%BA_%D0%91%D0%B0%D1%88%D1%8D%D0%B2%D1%96%D1%81_%D0%97%D1%8B%D0%BD%D0%B3%D0%B5%D1%80" title="Ісак Башэвіс Зынгер — Belarusian (Taraškievica orthography)" lang="be-tarask" hreflang="be-tarask" class="interlanguage-link-target">Беларуская (тарашкевіца)</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-bg"><a href="https://bg.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%98%D1%81%D0%B0%D0%BA_%D0%91%D0%B0%D1%88%D0%B5%D0%B2%D0%B8%D1%81_%D0%A1%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B3%D0%B5%D1%80" title="Исак Башевис Сингер — bulgare" lang="bg" hreflang="bg" class="interlanguage-link-target">Български</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-bn"><a href="https://bn.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E0%A6%86%E0%A6%87%E0%A6%9C%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%95_%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%AD%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B8_%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%99%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%97%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0" title="আইজাক বাশেভিস সিঙ্গার — bengali" lang="bn" hreflang="bn" class="interlanguage-link-target">বাংলা</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-br"><a href="https://br.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isaac_Bashevis_Singer" title="Isaac Bashevis Singer — breton" lang="br" hreflang="br" class="interlanguage-link-target">Brezhoneg</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ca"><a href="https://ca.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isaac_Bashevis_Singer" title="Isaac Bashevis Singer — catalan" lang="ca" hreflang="ca" class="interlanguage-link-target">Català</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-cs"><a href="https://cs.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isaac_Bashevis_Singer" title="Isaac Bashevis Singer — tchèque" lang="cs" hreflang="cs" class="interlanguage-link-target">Čeština</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-cy"><a href="https://cy.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isaac_Bashevis_Singer" title="Isaac Bashevis Singer — gallois" lang="cy" hreflang="cy" class="interlanguage-link-target">C